304
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,510
I didn't ask them;

305
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,720
they just have kind hearts.

306
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,750
Bai Lingling, listen to me.

307
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:35,120
