308
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:38,240
If you want to keep
the luminous pearl for yourself,

309
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:40,150
I advise you to give up.

310
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,600
Don't forget.

311
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,080
I'm here on a mission.

312
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:46,440
If my boss wants that pearl,

313
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,390
I will take it.

314
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:50,750
Fine.

315
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:52,910
Then let's see

316
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:55,510
if you can do that.

317
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:13,500
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

318
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:18,860
